Traitor
There is a traitor in the Animal Lord camp, no doubt about it. He could be found by telling everyone that a cache of money was found in the forest. Whoever comes to the cache is the traitor.
#subobj 1
Enter the ravine
The entrance to the ravine is next to the road to the Green Clan headquarters.
#subobj 2
Find the cache
The traitor's cache is hidden at the end of the ravine southwest of the Karansula Estate.
#subobj 3
Take the money
The animal lords will be very grateful to whoever returns their money to them!